Levitt Says UBS Leaders Will Lose Jobs Over Trade: Audio

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-19T13:22:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/levitt-says-ubs-leaders-will-lose-jobs-over-trade-audio.html
Arthur Levitt , a former chairman of
the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, says leaders of UBS
"are going to pay the price" for an unauthorized trade that cost
the company $2.3 billion. Levitt talks with Bloomberg's Ken 
Prewitt and Tom Keene on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:51
 